<span id="freeTextContainer6090769332420275654">&quot;<i>Aguntate tantito y la fruta caer en tu mano</i>,&quot; her father said. &quot;Wait a little while and the fruit will fall into your hand. You must be patient, Esperanza.&quot;<br/><br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/89763.Esperanza_Rising' title='Esperanza Rising by Pam Mu√±oz Ryan' rel='nofollow noopener'>Esperanza Rising</a> is my 2nd book of <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/1244538.Pam_Mu_oz_Ryan' title='Pam Mu√±oz Ryan' rel='nofollow noopener'>Pam Mu√É¬±oz Ryan</a>. The 1st book was the awesome <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22749539.Echo' title='Echo by Pam Mu√±oz Ryan' rel='nofollow noopener'>Echo</a>. <br/><br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/89763.Esperanza_Rising' title='Esperanza Rising by Pam Mu√±oz Ryan' rel='nofollow noopener'>Esperanza Rising</a> has been a wonderful read. One of the first thoughts I had, after finishing the book, was that, this book should have been slightly more longer.<br/><br/><i>Did you know if you lie down on the ground and stay very still, you can feel the Earth&apos;s heart </i></span>
  <span id="freeText6090769332420275654" style="display:none">"<i>Aguntate tantito y la fruta caer en tu mano</i>," her father said. "Wait a little while and the fruit will fall into your hand. You must be patient, Esperanza."<br /><br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/89763.Esperanza_Rising" title="Esperanza Rising by Pam Mu√±oz Ryan" rel="nofollow noopener">Esperanza Rising</a> is my 2nd book of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/1244538.Pam_Mu_oz_Ryan" title="Pam Mu√±oz Ryan" rel="nofollow noopener">Pam Mu√É¬±oz Ryan</a>. The 1st book was the awesome <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22749539.Echo" title="Echo by Pam Mu√±oz Ryan" rel="nofollow noopener">Echo</a>. <br /><br /><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/89763.Esperanza_Rising" title="Esperanza Rising by Pam Mu√±oz Ryan" rel="nofollow noopener">Esperanza Rising</a> has been a wonderful read. One of the first thoughts I had, after finishing the book, was that, this book should have been slightly more longer.<br /><br /><i>Did you know if you lie down on the ground and stay very still, you can feel the Earth's heart beating?</i><br /><br />This book is the story of Esperanza Ortega, whose life changes from a Fairytale existence to one filled with hardships and difficulties. It is about the changing attitudes of Esperanza and her understanding of Life. <br /><br />In Spanish, Esperanza means <b>Hope!!!</b><br /><br /><i>There is no rose without thorns...</i><br /><br />This story is about Faith, Belief, Dreams, Hope and Survival!<br /><br />The greatest message of this book is:<br /><br /><b>Do not ever be afraid to start over...</b></span>
